    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>HomeGrown</i> is a  casual farming game with satisfying clicker-style mechanics. Grow veg in your backyard, sell at the local town, then use that cash strategically as you choose from hundreds of upgrades to continuously scale up production!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/206389fcf7f56dbbf9ba144de4f096e5.poster.avif?t=1769421306\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/206389fcf7f56dbbf9ba144de4f096e5.webm?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/206389fcf7f56dbbf9ba144de4f096e5.mp4?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farming in <i>HomeGrown</i> is delightfully minimalistic. Just click to plant seeds, water crops, harvest produce, and tend to your garden. There are no overwhelming menus or steep learning curves - just jump in at any time and start clicking away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/cc4580c0355bccb459c6c5db7b92e994.poster.avif?t=1769421306\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/cc4580c0355bccb459c6c5db7b92e994.webm?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/cc4580c0355bccb459c6c5db7b92e994.mp4?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The local town offers unique ways to turn your harvest into profit. Trade at the weekly farmers’ market, fulfill special orders, win vegetable competitions, or sell to local stores to build up your farming business. Choose wisely to get the most cash for your crops!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/822e80c28a7d916e989edb0a731b2113.poster.avif?t=1769421306\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/822e80c28a7d916e989edb0a731b2113.webm?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/822e80c28a7d916e989edb0a731b2113.mp4?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've made some cash, it's time to spend it! Upgrade everything from tools and fertilizers to machinery and automation systems. With every investment your farming efficiency improves, allowing you to scale up production. There are constantly new perks to unlock - so you can just keep growing and growing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/6f4abffb48cdead3e6bc6b8955a9d431.poster.avif?t=1769421306\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/6f4abffb48cdead3e6bc6b8955a9d431.webm?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1894560/extras/6f4abffb48cdead3e6bc6b8955a9d431.mp4?t=1769421306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're after a relaxing experience or a deeper strategy challenge, it's totally up to you. Farm your own way - one satisfying click at a time!</p>",
